<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>activation email</title>
    <style>
        .email-page{
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 300px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 2px;
            padding: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .email-content{
            width: 100%;
            padding: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 1px;
        }
        .mail-activation-code{
            font-size: 2em;
            color: rgb(7, 7, 168);
        }
        .email-header{
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding:10px 20px;
            background-color: rgb(117, 17, 211);
        }
        .email-footer{
            text-align: start;
            padding: 5px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-page">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h3>Welcome to our Libraricals Resume builder</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="email-content">
            <p>Hello Mr/Miss , <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Thanks you request for updation. To change your account details, please use the following activation code.</p>
            <h3 class="mail-activation-code"><%= activationCode %></h3>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a Libraricals Resume account , please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any question, please don't forgot to contact us at <a href="mailto:softwares@engineer.com">softwares@engineer.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>